aspose.cells
Class CellArea

Represent an area of cells.

Example:

//Create Cell Area
$ca = new cells\CellArea();
$ca->StartRow = 0;
$ca->EndRow = 0;
$ca->StartColumn = 0;
$ca->EndColumn = 0;
